716663f-a.folder: Beekman Street & Pearl Street, Manhattan, NY
716663f-a.text:
99-103 Beekman Street, at, adjoining the S.W. corner of Pearl Street. The view shows the Second and Third Ave., Elevated on Pearl Street.
About 1923.
Gift of E. M. Jenk.
